Tr80646.@label: Fig 1.  Phylogenetic relationships of Morchella inferred from ITS and RPB1 sequences via parsimony (MP) and Bayesian (BI) analysis. Bootstrap values ≥50 % and Bayesian posterior probabilities (≥0.9) for internal nodes are given on the branches (MP/BI). Phylogenetically distinct species within this clade are identified according to Taşkin et al. (2010) and Du et al. (2012).
